v%E1%BA%A5n/poem-xfUL0RFU1M6WV9XOi__Sxg">Thiên vấn - 天問</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/author-2RPFDWkSQLaYkT3rYIGIrQ">Khuất Nguyên</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/Trung-thu-d%E1%BA%A1-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i-Quan-vi%C3%AAn-t%E1%BB%A9c-c%E1%BA%A3nh/poem-AEC6I0cqYu-k5cNGd4tJCw">Trung thu dạ Đại Quan viên tức cảnh - 中秋夜大觀園即景</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/author-1DK3jrzNRQ6A5gusK7iSPw">Tào Tuyết Cần</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/Xu%C3%A2n-d%E1%BA%A1-y%E1%BA%BFn-%C4%91%C3%A0o-l%C3%BD-vi%C3%AAn-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-auxHeWp2g4K7DVb1YesAww">Xuân dạ yến đào lý viên tự - 春夜宴桃李園序</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Bi%E1%BB%87n-Vinh/Xu%C3%A2n-du-%C4%91%E1%BB%93/poem-qH6rn0jHIxGzKVbzbRlRJA">Xuân du đồ - 春遊圖</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Bi%E1%BB%87n-Vinh/author-QKyM7SoFCzI5hQwR-YTzUA">Biện Vinh</a>)<br></div>	</div>
